name: The life of objects
description:
A particular familiar object has been around for 25 years. How many centuries will it be before it disappears? I have change. This just isn´t normal. Objects should at least take their share of the responsibilities. That is all I have against the inanimate world. 

“Cool memories” – Jean Baudrillard


digital painting  /  4100 x 4286 px  /  300 dpi  /  2022  /  from "Cool memories" series
